      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was out for a run in stanley park and i totally wiped out. my left ankle is huge right now and it's super swollen. i tried to walk it off but i literally can't put any weight on it at all without it feeling like it's going to snap. u think i just need to do the RICE thing for a few days and it'll be fine?",
