      "content": "but i already checked and i can move my toes fine and it doesnt look deformed or anything, so it's probably not broken. if i just stuck to the RICE method and maybe used a brace for a week, isn't that basically the same as what a doctor would tell me to do anyway? i really think i can just manage this myself with some rest.",
